NextAuth.js
------------
a open-source Authentication solution for next.js 
: Authentication
: Session management ( Token --> Session )
: different social providers (google/github/facebook)
: also credential based login support 

1. providers    : how uses authenticate, either with google/github / credentials
2. session strategy   : where session data(login user data) ,either jwt token /database
3. callback    : customize how data is handled in various points (token contents, where token storing)
4. pages    : auth pages (eg: login , error)